channel.title: Error_game_js5connect Error
channel.description:
Okay, I am a beginner at making RS Private servers. Every time I try to use a Client such as the "508 HD Client" what happens is it loads up the thing then says Connecting to upload server and it stops there and gives me the Error: Error_game_js5connect.
If anyone could help it would be appreciated ^.^

item.title: Error_game_js5connect Error
item.dc:creator: @Epic_Ancient Epic Ancient
item.description:
@Epic_Ancient wrote:

If you used Tonypker’s 508 HD Setup Tutorial With Pics, it won’t work. There’s a ton of files messed up with it.

If you’re trying to play a server, it’s either off, won’t work, or quit running.
